    "description": {
      "value": "<p>By 13th level, your tinkerings blend with magic and the arcane more and more. If you craft a magic item with a rarity of rare, it takes you a quarter of the normal time, and it costs you half as much of the usual gold.</p><p>When you cast an artificer spell with a casting time of one action, you can cast a cantrip of a casting time of one action as a bonus action.</p><p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your Intelligence modifier (minimum of once). You regain all expended uses when you finish a long rest.</p>",
